加分割线。\n\n:::: demo-wrapper no-padding\n  ::: center\n  ![hero](https://ccccooh.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20250226091515.png){ align=\"center\" }\n  :::\n::::\n\n不过这样就需要添加一堆`Divider组件`，还是有点儿麻烦，一种更加简单的办法是使用`Space`组件。\n\n我们可以在`src/components`文件夹下新建一个`Space.vue`组件，然后修改`App.vue`的代码。\n\n::: code-tabs\n\n@tab Space.vue\n```vue {4-10}\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <el-slider v-model=\"size\" style=\"width:50%\" />\n    <el-space :size=\"size\">\n      <el-link>链接一</el-link>\n      <el-link>链接二</el-link>\n      <el-link>链接三</el-link>\n      <el-link>链接四</el-link>\n      <el-link>链接五</el-link>\n    </el-space>\n  </div>\n</template>\n<script>\n  export default {\n    data() {\n      return {\n        size: 50,\n      };\n    },\n  };\n</script>\n```\n\n@tab app.vue\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div id=\"app\">\n    <Space />\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script>\n  import Space from \"./components/Space.vue\";\n\n  export default {\n    name: \"App\",\n    components: {\n      Space,\n    },\n  };\n</script>\n```\n\n:::\n\n运行效果如下：\n\n::: demo-wrapper no-padding\n![20250226145633](https://ccccooh.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20250226145633.png)\n:::\n\n拖动`Slider`后`size`会跟着变化，间隔也会发生变化。","excerpt":"","includedFiles":[],"tasklistId":0,"title":"","headers":[]}}
